
This directory contain a few EZWGL demos.

REdit     --- Resource Editor

DnD       --- Drag and drop demos.

GL        --- GL demos.

Message   --- Messages.

animate.c --- animation button
btnbox.c  --- button box

counter.c --- counter widget (example of composite widget)
locator.c --- locator (example of primitive widget)

puzzle.c  --- the 15 puzzle.
clock.c   --- digital clock (lcd widget)
hanoi.c   --- hanoi tower (workArea widget)
meter.c   --- status meter (statusMeter widget)
